headline: Super Micro Computer (SMCI) Teams Up with Ericsson to Power Edge AI with 5G Connectivity
summary: Super Micro Computer, Inc. (NASDAQ:SMCI) is one of the 10 AI Stocks on Wall Street’s Radar. On Tuesday, June 10th, Super Micro Computer, Inc. (NASDAQ:SMCI) and Ericsson (NASDAQ: ERIC) announced their intent to enter into a strategic collaboration that aims to accelerate Edge AI deployment.
